data.description: Welcome home to fabulous Tierra Santa in sunny North Las Vegas! This premier location is conveniently located just minutes from everything, including the VA Hospital, schools, parks, dining and more! The gated community offers a sparkling swimming pool, BBQ area, and a community park with a low monthly HOA fee. This immaculate 3-bedroom home has plenty of room for all your needs. The thoughtful floorplan has a huge great room with vaulted ceilings, large dining room and chef’s kitchen, and 3 spacious bedrooms on the 2nd floor. The main living area is well lit and very wide open. Tons of storage throughout, with durable low-maintenance hard surface flooring throughout, and no wasted space. The kitchen has  ample room for both meal prep and everyday dining at the island. The 3-car tandem garage offers plenty of room for storage, vehicles, or project workspace, and solar panels provide a welcome offset to rising utility rates, and let you spend money on things you truly enjoy instead!
